<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q28_v2" title="Q28_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceD</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>En la etiqueta de un preparado para té helado se indica la siguiente recomendación: mezclar <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas de polvo por cada <m:math><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math> mL de agua.</p>
    <p>Una persona quiere preparar <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> mL de té helado usando la misma mezcla de polvo y agua.</p>
    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes cantidades de cucharadas mantiene la misma proporción que la indicada en la etiqueta?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-prompt>Seleccione una opción.</qti-prompt>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA"><m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. La etiqueta indica <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> cucharadas por mL. Para <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> mL se debe multiplicar por <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>, porque <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math>. Entonces se necesitan <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas, no <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB"><m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si se usan <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas para <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> mL, la razón sería <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>100</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. La etiqueta exige <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Como <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, para <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> mL deberían ser <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas, no <m:math><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">1 cucharada<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Con <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> cucharada en <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> mL, la proporción sería <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, pero la etiqueta indica <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Además, como <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math>, la cantidad de polvo también debe multiplicarse por <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>: <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD"><m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Como <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math>, el agua es <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math> veces la cantidad original. Para mantener la misma proporción, las cucharadas también se multiplican por <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>: <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math>. Por eso, <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas mantiene la misma mezcla.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso: proporcionalidad directa</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar la proporción dada</strong></p>
            <p>La etiqueta recomienda <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas por cada <m:math><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math> mL de agua.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Comparar la nueva cantidad de agua con la original</strong></p>
            <p>Se quiere preparar <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> mL.</p>
            <p>Calculamos cuántas veces cabe <m:math><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math> en <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math>:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>600</m:mn><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> mL es <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math> veces <m:math><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:math> mL.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Mantener la misma proporción</strong></p>
            <p>Si la cantidad de agua se multiplica por <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>, la cantidad de cucharadas también debe multiplicarse por <m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:math>.</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificar con la razón</strong></p>
            <p>La razón original es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Con <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas y <m:math><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:math> mL, la razón es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mn>600</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>200</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, la proporción se mantiene.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La cantidad que mantiene la misma proporción es <m:math><m:mn>9</m:mn></m:math> cucharadas.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>